    "description": "Reliance Footprint Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Floor Manager at our Chandigarh location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Reliance Footprint Holdings Services:\nReliance Footprint Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chandigarh, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reliance Footprint Holdings Services!",
